COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x102
STRING: [Torta] “Just a minute.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x154
STRING: [Torta] “Sorry to keep you waiting. You're a little early
today.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x172
STRING: [Chris] “I guess.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x188
STRING: We were practicing at my house today.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x194
STRING: Chris was rarely late at times like these.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1a0
STRING: He always took it easy and slept until the last minute
when practice was at his place, but when it was at my
house, he was usually on time, even a little early.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1f6
STRING: [Ninna] “I'm glad to see you, Chris.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x228
STRING: [Chris] “Hello. Thank you for having me again today.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x246
STRING: [Ninna] “Long time no see.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x25c
STRING: Grandma said this while looking slightly to the side.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x272
STRING: Couldn't she even see the direction Chris was in today?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x27e
STRING: She seemed fine until the morning...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2ae
STRING: [Chris] “Huh? Oh, it has been two weeks, but every
week...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2d6
STRING: [Ninna] “It's fine.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x2f4
STRING: [Ninna] “So will you let me hear your practice again
today?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x326
STRING: [Chris] “Oh... Yes. Our performance is still poor, and we
only practice the one song, so I'm sure it won't be very
interesting.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x350
STRING: [Torta] “Hey, Chris!

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x376
STRING: I'm singing with you, so stop talking so humbly. And
why do you always speak so formally when you first get
here?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x39e
STRING: [Ninna] “Hee hee...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3d0
STRING: [Chris] “Well, let's get to it. We have to practice a lot
today to make up for tomorrow.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x3f0
STRING: [Torta] “A commendable idea. That means I have to get
fired up, too.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x410
STRING: Then we started our second practice in front of my
grandma.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x462
STRING: Silence descended on the room.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x476
STRING: What broke it was Grandma's applause.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x49e
STRING: [Ninna] “You've gotten even better. So much better than
before.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4b4
STRING: [Torta] “Thanks...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4de
STRING: It was just one song, but I felt more tired than usual.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x4f4
STRING: It wasn't quite nervousness, but we definitely felt a
satisfaction from accomplishing something.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x50a
STRING: It was true that my grandma wasn't an expert on music.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x516
STRING: But she went out to concerts every week.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x52c
STRING: Because of that knowledge and the experience of
hearing so much music, she had a slightly more attuned
ear than a normal person.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x542
STRING: So it made me truly happy to receive applause from my
grandmother.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x558
STRING: I wondered if I felt the same when Ms. Cordell praised
us.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x580
STRING: [Chris] “Thank you very much. But, we can't be satisfied
yet.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5bc
STRING: [Ninna] “That's only natural. But wasn't that the best
performance you could give, under the current
circumstances?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x5dc
STRING: [Torta] “Maybe. But you shouldn't praise Chris too
much. He slacks off from practice as soon as he does
well.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x618
STRING: [Chris] “Umm...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x646
STRING: Anyway. Last time was the same, but do you mind if we
practice normally?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x664
STRING: [Ninna] “Of course not. I'll do the cooking again today,
so I'll excuse myself now.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6a0
STRING: [Chris] “Isn't is still early? I just got here.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6be
STRING: [Ninna] “I'm making something a little different today. It
will take a lot of time and effort.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x6de
STRING: [Torta] “And it's the kitchen, right? We'll practice here,
so I'm sure you'll hear.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x706
STRING: [Ninna] “Yeah. I heard you well last time, I'm not worried
about that.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x734
STRING: Grandma went into the kitchen with her normal,
confident stride.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x74a
STRING: She'd said her legs hurt on rainy days, but it almost
never rained, so it was nothing to worry about.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x77c
STRING: [Chris] “I thought so last time, too, but I'm glad Ninna
seems healthy.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x79c
STRING: [Torta] “Her legs seem to have good days and bad days.
It's mostly good when you visit, Chris. So it would be
nice if you came by a little more often.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x7e2
STRING: [Chris] “As much as I can...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x7f8
STRING: [Torta] “Thanks. Okay, let's continue our practice.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x82a
STRING: [Chris] “Yeah-yeah.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x884
STRING: [Ninna] “Now then.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8ae
STRING: We'd finished cleaning up after dinner, and the three of
us talked with drinks in our hands.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8c4
STRING: Then Grandma suddenly said something.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8d8
STRING: [Ninna] “Now, I have a special present for the two of
you today.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x8f8
STRING: [Torta] “A present?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x92a
STRING: [Chris] “Could that be what you said you owed me? You
didn't have to...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x966
STRING: [Ninna] “Even so, it's like a hand-me-down; I can't go so
I was hoping that you would.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x986
STRING: Just like Chris, I didn't know what she was talking
about.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x99c
STRING: She didn't say anything to me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x9b0
STRING: [Ninna] “Did you know there's a performance at the
Concert Hall tomorrow? I have two tickets for it.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x9e4
STRING: [Torta] “What? But that's the performance that you look
forward to every year, Grandma...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa04
STRING: It was a concert performed at Natale by a gathering of
the school's alumni.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa1a
STRING: Most of the tickets were given to concerned parties,
and I'd heard that almost no regular people attended.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa30
STRING: Luckily Grandma was friendly with the man selling
tickets at the Concert Hall and she got them special.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa50
STRING: It was her yearly tradition to go to that concert with
Mrs. Maier on Natale.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xa6e
STRING: [Ninna] “I can go next year and the year after that. You
two have never been, have you? This year is your last
here, so it's perfect.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xab4
STRING: [Chris] “But, we have practice.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xae6
STRING: [Ninna] “Listening to good music is a form of practice.
Didn't you learn that?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb18
STRING: [Chris] “We did learn that.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb4a
STRING: [Ninna] “It's a group made up of the school's alumni, so
listening to them before your graduation recital could
never be a bad thing.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb74
STRING: [Torta] “But, two tickets?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xb92
STRING: [Ninna] “I was thinking of going with you, Torta. But
now you have a splendid partner, so go with him.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbc4
STRING: [Chris] “Umm... I shouldn't.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xbe2
STRING: [Ninna] “Chris...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc0c
STRING: Grandma's voice wasn't especially loud, and her tone
wasn't stern either.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc22
STRING: But Chris withered at that single word.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc36
STRING: [Ninna] “You will go.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc4c
STRING: [Torta] “Chris... It's no use. You know how stubborn
Grandma is.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xc88
STRING: [Chris] “Right...

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcb6
STRING: Thank you very much.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcca
STRING: [Ninna] “Yes, you're welcome. The concert starts at
three o'clock, so if you're going to Mass, go early.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xcea
STRING: [Torta] “So, can you come early in the morning?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd00
STRING: I remembered something about those two tickets.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd0c
STRING: I'd ask her about it later, but now I had to give up on it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd22
STRING: No... Forget giving up, I was actually happy.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd36
STRING: [Chris] “I suppose I could, what time?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd4c
STRING: [Torta] “Nine o'clock, I think.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd7e
STRING: [Chris] “That's early...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xd94
STRING: [Torta] “Even though you're always up that early with
Arie. Is there something wrong with me?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xdbc
STRING: [Chris] “No...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xdd2
STRING: [Torta] “So you can wake up, right?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe04
STRING: [Chris] “＊sigh＊ I was thinking I could sleep in this year.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe40
STRING: [Ninna] “Oh, and you don't have to dress formally, but
you should come in your uniform.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe60
STRING: [Torta] “Oh, that's true.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe7e
STRING: [Chris] “Understood. Okay, I'll go home soon... I have an
early start tomorrow.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xe9e
STRING: [Torta] “Ah-ha-ha. Well, that's fine.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xed0
STRING: [Ninna] “Okay. Well, see you tomorrow.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xeee
STRING: [Chris] “Where should we meet?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf04
STRING: When I was thinking of what time, Grandma spoke up
before me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf22
STRING: [Ninna] “Why don't you come pick her up?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf54
STRING: [Chris] “Alright... I'll be here at nine.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf6a
STRING: [Torta] “Oh, will you really come?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xf9c
STRING: [Chris] “Looks like I don't have a choice.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfb2
STRING: [Torta] “That's not very nice.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xfe4
STRING: [Chris] “I'm kidding... I was thinking I'd pick you up
anyway.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0xffa
STRING: [Torta] “Liar.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1018
STRING: [Ninna] “Hee hee.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1036
STRING: [Chris] “It doesn't matter. So here tomorrow at nine
o'clock?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x104c
STRING: [Torta] “Yeah-yeah. You can't come in normal clothes.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x106a
STRING: [Chris] “Yeah-yeah.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1080
STRING: Chris answered like that, and laughed a little as he left.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10aa
STRING: [Torta] “So... Grandma?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10c0
STRING: After the door was completely closed, I turned to my
grandma to make sure.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x10fc
STRING: [Ninna] “Hmm? What is it?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1112
STRING: [Torta] “Those tickets... Are they from Mrs. Maier?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1144
STRING: [Ninna] “Yeah... So you remembered?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x115a
STRING: [Torta] “So this is what you were talking about then.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x118c
STRING: [Ninna] “That makes things easier, then. Go and enjoy
yourself. It'll be a good experience.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11ac
STRING: [Torta] “But... You were looking forward to it.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11ca
STRING: [Ninna] “I'm looking forward to you and Chris more,
Torta.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x11ea
STRING: [Torta] “You may feel that way, Grandma... But Mrs.
Maier...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1208
STRING: [Ninna] “She feels the same. She cares about you, Torta.
She says she looks forward to coming here, like you're
her own granddaughter.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1232
STRING: [Torta] “But...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1250
STRING: [Ninna] “She gladly gave it up for your love life, Torta.
You can't let that go to waste.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1270
STRING: [Torta] “Love... That's...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x12a2
STRING: [Ninna] “You like Chris, don't you Torta?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x12b8
STRING: [Torta] “...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x12ea
STRING: [Ninna] “It's okay, I know that much. But is it about Arie?

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1300
STRING: [Torta] “Yeah...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1316
STRING: Grandma got right to the core of it like that.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x132a
STRING: [Ninna] “Torta. Listen to me. Chris comes by often now,
right?”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x134a
STRING: [Torta] “Yeah...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1368
STRING: [Ninna] “I'm sure you already know, but that boy has
gotten happier.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1390
STRING: [Ninna] “It's totally different than when he first came
here. And I know just who to thank for that.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13b0
STRING: [Torta] “That's not me.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13c6
STRING: It was the illusion of Arie I made inside myself.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13d2
STRING: Chris depended on that.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x13e6
STRING: [Ninna] “It is you. It's not Arietta. Arietta can't do that
anymore.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1406
STRING: [Torta] “But...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1424
STRING: [Ninna] “But nothing. Listen.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x143a
STRING: [Torta] “Yes, ma'am...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1458
STRING: [Ninna] “Torta. Think of yourself more. Not for Arietta,
and not for Chris. Do something for yourself.”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1482
STRING: [Torta] “Grandma...”

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14a6
STRING: That wasn't it.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14ba
STRING: I just kept apologizing in my heart.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14ce
STRING: I was always lying for my own desires.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14ee
STRING: For Chris.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x14fa
STRING: For Arietta.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1506
STRING: It was all lies. I liked Chris, and I wanted to be with him.
That's why I was his partner now.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1526
STRING: But I couldn't put that into words.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x1532
STRING: My tears just spilled over, and I felt that I was deceiving
my grandma who always worried about me.

COMMANDS.LABEL: 0x155a
STRING: My tears just wouldn't stop.
